OL,3,CWhy Starmer will struggle to survive
OL,4,Cthe Gorton humiliation
OL,6,FThere are three reasons why this is
OL,7,Fdeeply problematic for Starmer
OL,8,Fpersonally.
OL,10,FFirst, and perhaps of least
OL,11,Fimportance, the campaign it fought in
OL,12,Fthe constituency now looks ridiculous.
OL,13,FIt constantly made the claim that the
OL,14,FGreens were an irrelevance in the
OL,15,Fcontest and that the only way to beat
OL,16,FReform was to vote Labour.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772190104
OL,3,CWhy Starmer will struggle to survive
OL,4,Cthe Gorton humiliation
OL,6,FWell, it got one part of the analysis
OL,7,Fright: a majority in Gorton and Denton
OL,8,Fdid not want a Reform MP. But they
OL,9,Fchose Zack Polanski's Greens as the
OL,10,Fvehicle to achieve that, so
OL,11,Fdisillusioned are they with Starmer's
OL,12,Fgovernment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772190104
OL,3,CWhy Starmer will struggle to survive
OL,4,Cthe Gorton humiliation
OL,6,FSecond, Starmer himself - through a
OL,7,Fcommittee of Labour's ruling National
OL,8,FExecutive Committee - vetoed the
OL,9,Fstrongest potential candidate, Andy
OL,10,FBurnham, mayor of Greater Manchester.
OL,11,FWe'll never know whether Burnham's
OL,12,Fpersonal local popularity would have
OL,13,Freversed the anti-Labour tide, and
OL,14,Fwould have secured the seat. That's at
OL,15,FStarmer's door.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
