OL,3,CWhy Starmer will struggle to survive
OL,4,Cthe Gorton humiliation
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FSome Labour MPs will give him the
OL,12,Fbenefit of the doubt in those
OL,13,Frespects. But most will just be
OL,14,Ffrantically worried about their career
OL,15,Fprospects.
OL,17,FSo what follows from Labour's Gorton
OL,18,Fcatastrophe?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772190104
OL,3,CWhy Starmer will struggle to survive
OL,4,Cthe Gorton humiliation
OL,6,FFirst, the pressure for a massive
OL,7,Foverhaul of Labour's political
OL,8,Fpositioning and policies will become
OL,9,Firresistible.
OL,11,FSecond, Starmer's own credibility is
OL,12,Fnow so damaged that he will struggle
OL,13,Fto recover.
OL,15,FIf he has another roll of the dice
OL,16,Fbefore the local and national
OL,17,Felections on 7 May, it's only because
OL,18,Fno credible alternative candidate to
OL,19,Fbe leader is ready to launch a
OL,20,Fcampaign yet.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772190104
OL,3,CWhy Starmer will struggle to survive
OL,4,Cthe Gorton humiliation
OL,6,FBut even members of his cabinet say
OL,7,Fthat the consensus among Labour MPs is
OL,8,Fhe won't lead them into the next
OL,9,Felection. And when they say that so
OL,10,Fcasually, it's difficult to see how
OL,11,Feven Starmer - who prides himself on
OL,12,Fnever giving up - will keep on keeping
OL,13,Fon.
OL,15,FYou can hear Talking Politics wherever
OL,16,Fyou get your podcasts, including Apple
OL,17,FPodcasts and Spotify, and watch every
OL,18,Fepisode on YouTube and ITVX.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/11
